    "Next, we present applications of graph pooling methods.",
    "Following that, we conduct a comparative analysis of various graph pooling methods and evaluate their performance on benchmark datasets to provide a comprehensive understanding of their strengths and weaknesses.",
    "Finally, we analyze the current challenges of graph pooling methods and give future research directions.",
    "However, we acknowledge the lack of a unified standard or evaluation framework to compare the performance of various graph pooling methods, making it challenging to select the most suitable method for a particular application.",
    "Future research will focus on developing such a framework to enable more effective comparison and selection of graph pooling methods."
